# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#  AnymeX TODO Bot + Dashboard — Environment Variables
#  Copy this file to .env and fill in your values
#  cp .env.example .env
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━


# ── Discord Bot ─────────────────────────────────────
# Your bot token from Discord Developer Portal → Bot → Token
DISCORD_TOKEN=your_bot_token_here

# Your Discord server (guild) ID
# How to get: Right-click your server in Discord → Copy Server ID
# (Enable Developer Mode in Discord Settings → Advanced first)
DISCORD_GUILD_ID=your_guild_id_here


# ── Discord OAuth2 (for web dashboard login) ────────
# From Discord Developer Portal → Your App → General Information
DISCORD_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here

# From Discord Developer Portal → Your App → OAuth2 → Client Secret
DISCORD_CLIENT_SECRET=your_client_secret_here

# The URL Discord redirects to after login
# For local dev: http://localhost:8080/callback
# For production: https://your-render-url.onrender.com/callback
# ⚠️  Must also be added in Discord Dev Portal → OAuth2 → Redirects
DISCORD_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:8080/callback


# ── Flask ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Secret key for session encryption — generate with:
# python -c "import secrets; print(secrets.token_hex(32))"
FLASK_SECRET=generate_a_random_secret_here


# ── GitHub (data storage) ───────────────────────────
# Personal Access Token with repo read/write access
# Generate at: GitHub → Settings → Developer Settings → Personal Access Tokens → Fine-grained
# Required permissions: Contents (read & write)
GITHUB_TOKEN=your_github_pat_here

# The GitHub repo used as the database (owner/repo format)
DATA_OWNER=Shebyyy
DATA_REPO=anymex-support-db
DATA_BRANCH=main


# ── AI (Groq) ───────────────────────────────────────
# Used by the bot to auto-generate TODO titles from messages
# Get a free key at: https://console.groq.com
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here


# ── Discord Forum Channels ──────────────────────────
# IDs of your forum channels for bugs and suggestions
# How to get: Right-click the forum channel → Copy Channel ID
DISCORD_BUGS_CHANNEL_ID=your_bugs_forum_channel_id_here
DISCORD_SUGGESTIONS_CHANNEL_ID=your_suggestions_forum_channel_id_here


# ── Optional: Web Proxy ─────────────────────────────
# Only needed if your hosting provider requires outbound proxy
# Leave blank if not needed
# WEB_PROXY_HOST=
# WEB_PROXY_PORT=
# WEB_PROXY_USER=
# WEB_PROXY_PASS=


# ── Optional: Port override ─────────────────────────
# Default is 8080. Render sets this automatically.
# PORT=8080
